data.value:
Encrypts every single file under the target directory with AES algorithm for 3 times. Uses random cipher for every file. Once a folder is wiped with House Party Protocol it's irreversible.
While this may be helpful for some, there are significant risks. For one, in some countries you could go to jail on obstruction of justice charges just for running this program, even though you are innocent
House Party Protocol is not perfect. A skilled thief or law enforcement can disable it. Use with caution
